sp.p:
And if you pleaſe, let it goe to the Punkes delight;
'tis your onely ſweet tune: for women doe love the Punks
delight.

What, my fretfull Doctour? the only curer of mad
folks;


Know I my ſelfe?

To the Society at the Swan two pottles and a halfe:
Monkey the health; theſe are my noble & prime viſi tants;
the boxes I gave you to lay up.
